 at de n\u00e5 g\u00e5r inn i prosessen med erstatningssakene.", "Erstatningsbel\u00f8pene kommer til \u00e5 bli betydelige, if\u00f8lge Matre.", "(\u00a9NTB)"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|innenriks"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "5797e457d937577d6af105549c198c5ec582a9ca619484315f1317f258d68575"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-03-23T17:09:04.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Berge Gerdt Larsen fikk delvis medhold i skattesaken mot Skatt Vest i Borgarting lagmannsrett. En lang prosess g\u00e5r mot slutten, og Berge forbereder s\u00f8ksm\u00e5l."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://static.polarismedia.no/skins/prod/publication/adressa/gfx/applefavicon.png"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/605698f1d1045c4dd509372937858a1fc4652c81.jpg?58d40130"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Berge Gerdt Larsen fikk delvis medhold i skattesak -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "605698f1d1045c4dd509372937858a1fc4652c81"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "innenriks"]}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": ["larsen oil", "aberdeen ltd"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["dommen", "staten", "delvis", "saken", "delvis medhold", "lagmannsrett", "medhold", "skattesak"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["larsen", "gas", "gulating", "borgarting", "skattedirektoratet", "skatt vest"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "berge"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["gerdt larsen", "jan munthe magnus", "hugo matre"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value":